;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mGrid: 201Г—101 points with 10m spacing (2km Г— 1km domain)                                                    \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mVelocity: 1.5 km/s top layer, 3.5 km/s bottom layer (interface at 500m depth)                               \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mSources: 5 shots at 100m, 300m, 500m, 700m, 900m positions                                                  \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mReceivers: 100 receivers from 0m to 1980m with 20m spacing                                                  \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mRecording: 2 seconds at 4ms sampling (250 Hz)                                                               \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mWavelet: 15 Hz Ricker wavelet                                                                               \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m 4 \u001b[0m\u001b[1mData Access\u001b[0m:                                                                                                   \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mSynthetic data is stored in \u001b[1;36;40mdobs\u001b[0m (a \u001b[1;36;40mjudiVector\u001b[0m)                                                             \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mIndividual shot records can be accessed as \u001b[1;36;40mdobs.data[i]\u001b[0m                                                     \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33m   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;33m вЂў \u001b[0mEach shot record is a 501Г—100 matrix (time samples Г— receivers)                                             \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m                                                                                                                   \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m The code has been tested and runs successfully, generating 5 shot records of synthetic seismic data that you can  \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m analyze or use for further processing.                                                                            \u001b[93mв”‚\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[93mв•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[?25h"]
